function done = j_trajectory_2(t_1,t_2)
%UNTITLED3 Summary of this function goes here%   Detailed explanation goes here
    r_1 = t_2(1)-t_1(1);
    r_2=t_2(2)-t_1(2);
    r_3=t_2(3)-t_1(3);  
    f= @(x)[t_1(1)+x*r_1,t_1(2)+x*r_2,t_1(3)+x*r_3];
    done=f;
